platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Intuitive deck building, a sinister game show setting, and snarky quips from a malevolent Lady Luck keep us coming back to roll the dice in this fantastic roguelike.
De la construction de deck intuitive, une ambiance sinistre de jeu tlvis et des remarques acerbes dune Dame Chance malveillante... On ne se lasse pas de lancer les ds de ce roguelike fantastique.
Intuitive deck building, a sinister game show setting and snarky quips from a malevolent Lady Luck keep us coming back to roll the dice in this fantastic roguelike.
